basics.name: Kelly Johanna Torres Navarro
basics.label: Web Developer
basics.summary: I'm a Telecommunications Engineer from the Univesity of Pamplona. I have four years of experience in web development with languages like PHP, Python, and Javascript. I have worked on multiple projects where I have worked as a Full Stack Developer, ensuring the application's requirements successfully. I'm interested in learning new technologies and strategies to do better and faster projects where I'm working.
